Package: sics
Title: Fit Models Under Linear Constraints Using Sampling-In-Constrained-Space
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Lukas", "Lengersdorff", , "lukaslengersdorff@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8750-5057"))
Description: Fits statistical models under linear constraints on a parameter, using STAN. Also provides methods to estimate Marginal Likelihoods/Bayes Factors for such models.
